
Ionic
opensource , mobile-optimized library for building apps with html,js,css
built on top of angularjs
built specifically for Cordova apps to make use of native device features

Cordova
javascript api that wraps native apis E.g camera, scanner

============== installations ================
npm install ionic -g
npm install cordova -g

========== create an app ===============
ionic start scheduler blank


========= start the app ================
ionic serve

======== add dev platform =============
ionic platform add android

=====  (For running say customed query to extract local data from say db) ==========================
bower install lodash --save-dev

===== Angular Cache () ==========================
bower install angular-cache --save-dev

===== angular for google maps (http://angular-ui.github.io/angular-google-maps/#!/api) ===========
bower install angular-google-maps --save-dev


